make sure you use VsCode for code editor and these Vscode extension
+ Prettier //code formatter
+ Eslint //highlights unused and unwanted code


>> Project setup : 
Use these commands to install project
=====================================

# Check the version of react and node. This needs to be same for every developer.
# npx create-react-app [name of project] 
# cd  [name of project]  <!--move to the project-->
# npm i antd  <!-- we will use antd as a UI library-->
# npm i node-sass <!-- for using SCSS format, this is required-->
# npm i react-router-dom <!-- for routing we will use this library-->
# npm start  <!-- start project.-->
#
=================================
Or you can take pull from gitlab  
=================================
Login to gitlab
Take pull from project url
git clone project url
move to folder
npm i
npm i node-sass // this command should be run
npm start  // start project.

=================================
Folder structure: 
=================================

|--Node_module 
|--Public 
|--Src
    |--Assets
        |--images <!-- all the images/ image folder will go here -->
        |--scss-component <!-- ants component's css is here component wise -->
            |--
        |--variables
            |--
        bootstrap.css
        global.scss
    |--Components
        |--auth
        |--error page <!-- all the error pages  -->
        |--landing page <!--allcms pages like home, about, contact etc can be created here --> 
        |--layout <!-- --> 
        |--ui-component <!-- ui compoenent can be manipulated from here --> 
            |--Button
            |--Form
            |--Image
            |--Text
        |--utilities <!--  --> 
            |--Alert
            |--Loader
            |--Notification
    |--Routes
        |--index <!-- all routes path here --> 
        |--routes based on userlogin
    |--Theme <!--for changing the theme light/dark -->
    |--Services <!--APIs list here -->
    |--Utils
        |--Authcontext <!--this maintain the user detail throughout the platform -->
        |--Constant <!--we can declare the constant for regex  and other variables that needs to be constant -->
        |--Helperfunction <!-- can declare the global function eg. addition/subtraction or changing anything -->
        |--Imagepath <!-- declare the image path here-->
    |--App
    |--index
|--Gitignore <!--all the images folderwise-->
|--Package.lock.json
|--package.json